{"build_type":"executable","description":"Build the package dependency-relation graph for a set of roots and emit it as JSON on stdout. Request (argv[1]): {\"build-package-dependency-relation-graph\":{\"roots\":[\"<dir>\",...]}}. Enumerates+collects the graph in RAM via collect_dependency_graph_from_roots and prints the graph array unformatted to fd 1. No output file, no stdin. Bad request (no argv, unparseable, no arg object, no roots field) → clean JSON {error} on stdout, exit 0, never a crash. Reuses parse_argument_vector_json_request, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, collect_dependency_graph_from_roots, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output, begin_empty_mapping_document_value, add_str_field.","module_name":"build-package-dependency-relation-graph","package_name":"build-package-dependency-relation-graph","function_definitions":{"build-package-dependency-relation-graph":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_roots","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"roots"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_error","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"error"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"m_badreq","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"build-package-dependency-relation-graph: request must be {\"build-package-dependency-relation-graph\": {\"roots\": [\"<dir>\", ...]}}"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"parse-argument-vector-json-request","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"__argc"},{"kind":"var","value":"__argv"}],"result_assignment_variable":"req","